window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p></p><p><b>They say bad things come in threes, and the De Luca brothers have trouble written all over them.</b></p><p>Matteo, Vito, Enzo. Their ruthless reputation has followed them all the way from Italy to New York City, and they're here to collect what they were promised.</p><p>I'm not supposed to care that they're enticing, my favorite kind of temptation. I'm here on a mission to wipe the slate of my sordid past clean.</p><p>But one taste is all it takes to have me questioning my plan. I'm sinking faster than I can piece together a way out.</p><p>Redemption has never tasted so bittersweet.</p><p><i>Redemption </i>is a why-choose standalone spin-off story from Featherstone Academy with hints of violence and steamy scenes.</p><p></p>"; 
